{"tid":1778294,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[翻兜世界大戰] SUV/Crossover vs 房車/旅行車","createTime":"2019-12-10T23:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T13:41:57.000Z","uid":236926,"like":17,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2cae8ec45896aeb1b075da30bfb05bbfc4a9a182","tid":1778294,"uid":236926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T23:43:46.000Z","msg":"最近繼三菱，Ford之後，澳洲車廠Holden都宣佈集中推出SUV車款(及澳洲獨有的Ute車款)並放棄續出期下剩餘車型<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.carthrottle.com/post/holden-is-dropping-cars-altogether-to-focus-on-suvs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.carthrottle.com%2Fpost%2Fholden-is-dropping-cars-altogether-to-focus-on-suvs%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=b5f50c3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.carthrottle.com/post/holden-is-dropping-cars-altogether-to-focus-on-suvs/</a><br />\n<br />\n現時大部分車廠都集中火力推出跑車化的SUV及Crossover車款(下至X3M X4M GLA45 AMG，上至Urus，RSQ8，Cayenne Coupe)，反而以前較主流嘅跑房車及跑車好似少左人提或揀，跑車/超跑級旅行車更只凈得兩間德國廠揀(Merc E63S Estate, Audi RS4, 6 Avant)<br />\n<br />\n而中小型SUV/Crossover車款現時的密集程度，甚至比同廠的房車/旅行車及掀背款有更多不同尺寸<br />\n電動車方面該情況更為嚴重<br />\n<br />\n想問各位對目前該趨勢的睇法<br />\nCrossover又應該是否取諦傳統車型？<br />\n<br />\n同埋睇睇大家支持邊面的走向<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正評: SUV, Crossover<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負評: 房車/旅行車"},{"pid":"fb62a53a0edb53d5ba6274522fc3d8a7288938bc","tid":1778294,"uid":13558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T00:54:06.000Z","msg":"造車技術好左，<br />\n好多suv都好揸好多，<br />\n又難怪多左人去揀嘅"},{"pid":"21a3c8f17220f5015a61f63c502fd7241b0492ff","tid":1778294,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T01:32:46.000Z","msg":"跑車/超跑級旅行車更只凈得兩間德國廠揀(Merc E63S Estate, Audi RS4, 6 Avant)<br />\n<br />\n姐係咁，寶馬/Alpina 就keep住有造touring版嘅"},{"pid":"5bda0627bfdc897872bf7a2b20d123765569839c","tid":1778294,"uid":72085,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T01:54:57.000Z","msg":"房車市場萎縮得好快，太唔實用，要跟車既人同物愈嚟愈多<br />\n仲要依家D車廠出SUV咁俾心機落料，咩款式咩尺寸都有，相反房車就hea整，點買得落手，每間大廠既SUV我都數得出有幾架係想要，房車真係冇乜，頂多係得某幾款王牌產品有興趣eg. G20, W213<br />\n不過有部分車廠係擺到明偷雞專出crossover SUV compact SUV 升高少少車身賣貴八萬"},{"pid":"d0e02cf38c8e4a277ebbb0837af1ffce6a0e14b2","tid":1778294,"uid":87172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T01:55:11.000Z","msg":"因為全世界既消費者(大部份)都覺得SUV好睇過旅行車, 咁撚簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36a174db80569e8974f1fccf4ff5ad060981cea","tid":1778294,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T01:59:02.000Z","msg":"香港用SUV off road好少,買返七座mpv至實際"},{"pid":"b57d9bcef0a99e6abe03e23649ee0e0013018c60","tid":1778294,"uid":33908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:02:13.000Z","msg":"台灣Ford 有mondeo wagon好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港40以下得部Mazda 6 wagon揀"},{"pid":"cf9114658953da34e308c8fb4fba08631a1fb462","tid":1778294,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57d9bcef0a99e6abe03e23649ee0e0013018c60","tid":1778294,"uid":33908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:02:13.000Z","msg":"台灣Ford 有mondeo wagon好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港40以下得部Mazda 6 wagon揀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"連登仔會話<br />\n<br />\n雙田維修手工錢平，間間車房都識整<br />\n雙田多零件，零件又平<br />\n雙田唔會壞，呢d啲垃圾牌子好易壞<br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲人可能一世人只養過雙田就亂鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ea22a2939f66b64e0ed5db3ba8a4fd12973877","tid":1778294,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf9114658953da34e308c8fb4fba08631a1fb462","tid":1778294,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57d9bcef0a99e6abe03e23649ee0e0013018c60","tid":1778294,"uid":33908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:02:13.00